@startuml
title Builder - Estrutura

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Cliente

interface Builder {
  + buildParteA(): Builder
  + buildParteB(): Builder
  + getResult(): Product
}

class ConcreteBuilder {
  - product: Product
  + buildParteA(): Builder
  + buildParteB(): Builder
  + getResult(): Product
}

class Product

class Director {
  + construct(builder: Builder): void
}

Cliente --> Director : usa
Cliente --> Builder : configura
Director --> Builder : orquestra etapas
ConcreteBuilder ..|> Builder
ConcreteBuilder --> Product : monta

note right of Director
  Encapsula uma sequência padrão
  de construção quando necessário.
end note

@enduml

@startuml
title Builder - Comunicação

actor Cliente
participant Director
participant ConcreteBuilder
participant Product

Cliente -> Director : construct(builder)
Director -> ConcreteBuilder : buildParteA()
Director -> ConcreteBuilder : buildParteB()
Cliente -> ConcreteBuilder : getResult()
ConcreteBuilder --> Cliente : Product
Cliente -> Product : usa objeto construído

@enduml
